room_title: Escape room "The Oval-ish Office" by Red Herring Escape Rooms in St. Louis
room_address: 6358 Delmar Boulevard, Suite 222, Delmar Loop, MO 63130
room_description:
What started out as a casual tour through the White House with your friends has turned into something much more serious. The President of the United States, who becomes trapped in an elevator while being whisked to the White House Situation Room by the Secret Service, informs you that the nation is in grave danger.
A submarine in the Pacific Ocean has launched a nuclear missile targeted right at the White House! The countdown is on as you and your team have 60 minutes to find the launch codes hidden throughout the Oval Office to activate the Steel Shield anti-ballistic missile system to save the nation's capital from destruction. And then you have to escape... Good luck.
